        <div class="corner-accent corner-accent-tl"></div>
        <div class="corner-accent corner-accent-br"></div>

        <p class="greeting">Hi {{ $json['cleaned_name'] }} team,</p>

        <p>Most firms hire more operations managers as they scale. That is a <strong>bug, not a feature.</strong></p>

