          <div class="list-item"><strong>4. Review developer timesheets and draft accurate invoices</strong> to flag inconsistencies early.</div>
        </div>

        <p class="cta">Are you open to a short Loom intro showing how this logic would work for {{ $json['cleaned_name'] }}?</p>

